        _CopyFilesMarkedCopyLocal - the ProjectReference
        _CopySourceItemsToOutputDirectory - the "Content" items above

       NOTE: This is not necessary. Our AfterBuild step ignores that output anyway.
             But it's cleaner and less confusing (no random Output\Release\DeleteMe.dll)             
  -->
